Automatically add tasks to My Day based on their due date, controlled by a global user setting. Currently, My Day shows due-today tasks via a query-level OR filter in `findMyDay()`, but doesn't set the `is_in_my_day` flag — so those tasks show "Add to My Day" even though they're visible, and Telegram's `/myday` command doesn't return them.

---

